{{flavour|A ring that increases the intelligence of its wearer.}}

A '''+6 ring of intelligence''' affects the [[intelligence]] of the wearer.

==Desirability==
Good for spellcasters. While +6 intelligence will always be worse than a [[ring of wizardry]] for decreasing failure rate, intelligence also increases [[spell power]]. Having more power means that spells are more effective, which is always useful.

Can also be used to prevent [[stat zero]] from having 0 intelligence. Other than that, it's useless for those who can't cast spells.

==History==
*Prior to [[0.27]], you could find rings of intelligence with a -4 enchantment; such rings were always [[curse]]d.
*Prior to [[0.25]], enchantment values ranged from 2 to 6 (positive and negative).

